Rattrap:




"Boy, did I come at da wrong place." he said, noticing the new 
arrivals. He jerked his head up to see Archangle take the new bot 
into the air. 

He reacted. "Rattrap, Maxim---" He paused. He didn't have Maximal 
programing at the moment. "...Terrorize." He transformed to robot 
mode and drew his gun on Archangle. He fired at him, with marksman 
aim.
